	- allow one nuisance parameter to control several correlation coefficients

2013-03-30 Kevin Kroeninger <kevin.kroeninger@phys.uni-goettingen.de>
	* examples/advanced/mvcombination:
	- added correlation coefficients as nuisance parameters
	- added an example input file for this new feature

