	* BCMath: added LogGammaPDF to BCMath.

2013-02-25 Frederik Beaujean <beaujean@mpp.mpg.de>
	* introduction: add warning for SetPrior*
	* BCParameter:
	  - use const qualifiers
	  - remove unnecessary ctors, dtor
	* BCModel: access BCParameter through const, so user code like model->GetParameter(i)->SetLimits(...) is illegal as it would bypass BCModel::SetParameterRange and MCMC is inconsistent. Requires changes in six other classes
	* BCEfficiencyFitter: fix warning and bug

2013-02-19 Frederik Beaujean <beaujean@mpp.mpg.de>
	* BCMath, fast fitters: clean up interfaces and $p$-value correction
	* introduction: describe new interfaces

